      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Home » Azure Automated Data Reporting For SLB"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Houston, Texas"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Oil and Energy"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Large Enterprise"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "SLB - Formerly Schlumberger"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "SLB (formerly known as Schlumberger) is a global technology company that leads innovation in the energy industry. They are headquartered in Houston, Texas. They operate in more than 100 countries, with an annual revenue of $36.07 billion, providing cutting-edge solutions to customers across the oil and gas, geothermal, carbon capture, and renewable energy sectors. They are committed to pioneering technological advancements to address the complex energy challenges globally."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/slb.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 267,
          "h": 267
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "THE PROBLEM"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Fragmented Data and Manual Reporting Bottlenecks"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Delayed data access slowed down managers in analyzing the data needed for critical business decisions"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Lack of tools made non-technical teams unable to generate their own reports"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual data extraction posed the constant risk of errors and discrepancies across reports"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inability to consolidate data from multiple sources to oversee a holistic business performance"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inefficient utilization of technical resources as they were constantly distracted by routine data extraction tasks from the DBAs"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The Oil Field Marketplace (OFMP) team at SLB saw itself at the crossroads of being unable to utilize operational data effectively. Data from Azure SQL Database and Google Analytics was siloed and demanded manual work for extraction and reporting. This continued dependence on the technical teams and DBAs to satisfy reporting needs created bottlenecks in the following areas:"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "GET A FREE DATA CONSULTATION",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "OUR SOLUTION"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "An End-To-End Automated Data Reporting Platform"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 partnered with SLB to design and implement an Azure-powered data ingestion and reporting solution:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Automated Data Ingestion  and Transformation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Centralized Data Lake"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Unified Visualization & Reporting  Using Power BI"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Utilizing Microsoft Azure’s data services (Azure Data Factory and Azure Databricks) to upgrade manual data consolidation to efficient data ingestion from Azure SQL Database and Google Analytics, and improving data quality, respectively.",
        "Serving as a central repository for all raw and processed data, laying down a secure and scalable foundation.",
        "Delineating complex operational data in interactive dashboards and reports using Power BI. This was made accessible through the OFMP portal."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Energy/Oil & Gas Dashboards & Reporting Suite"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Order Details"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Product Health"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Sales By Category/Product"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Sales Distribution"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "From order details to product health KPIs and sales realized per category/brand/product, and distribution is holistically reported through the dashboards backed by Power BI:",
        "Providing a detailed breakdown of order trends over time.",
        "Offering insights into product performance and lifecycle.",
        "Visualizing sales performance across different categories and individual products.",
        "Illustrating the geographical or channel-based spread of sales."
      ],
