    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Business Outcomes"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Self-Service Analytics"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Real-Time Visibility"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Improved Data Accuracy"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The implementation of an automated data reporting solution powered by Microsoft Azure Data Services delivered significant and measurable results to SLB’s OFMP team, giving them the ability to efficiently extract, transform, load and report their data.",
        "Gaining direct access to data and reporting tools reduced massive dependence on the technical teams and DBAs and increased their productivity by 5%.",
        "The creation of a unified reporting platform provided instant insights into key operational metrics such as:",
        "Achieved 99.9% data accuracy through automation of data ingestion and reporting, paving the way for more reliable data to work with."
      ],
      "listItems": [
        "Tracking and optimizing vendor contributions.",
        "Real-time tracking of order statuses and trends.",
        "Highlighting highly demanded products and market trends.",
        "Analyzing customer interactions and understanding their preferences."
      ],
      "ctas": [
        {
